name: HUMAN BEING - Black Heather Sweatshirt
description: If us Humans came in packets (like pretty much everything does these days) we reckon they would look something like this. After all we're a bit like the usual stuff that comes in big boxes... we're fragile, need to be kept dry, handled with care... And kept the right way up! Especially after a couple of cheeky beers! You can be a walking talking human box... Maybe a beat box... But we'll leave that choice to you! Hand printed in the UK on a BLACK HEATHER organic sweatshirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: ALL OVER PEACE
description: This is the second shirt of our collection that takes inspiration from the peace symbol. It is our debut in the world of all over pattern design. We're really pleased with how this has turned out. The peace sign is an iconic and powerful logo that works in a subtle manner when used all over! Hand printed in the UK on a NAVY BLUE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: THE DOVE II
description: This is a Bauhaus inspired/minimalist remix of our classic Dove design by Si Scott. It's still a big favourite of ours, so we thought we'd give it a slightly different interpretation! Hand printed in the UK on an ECRU organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: BELIEVE, CREATE, INSPIRE
description: We wanted a t-shirt that summed up our ethos and what makes us tick. So we've gone for three words that we think do just that. We believe, we create, we inspire. Hand printed in the UK on a HEATHER GREY organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: PEACE
description: "The state of harmony characterized by the lack of violence, conflict behaviors, and the freedom from fear of violence." The second shirt is 'Peace', based on the iconic peace symbol. Originally, it was designed as the logo for The British Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament in the late 1950s. Did you know that it is a combination of the semaphore signals for the letters N and D, standing for nuclear disarmament? See, we're not just a pretty face! We've taken the familiar peace sign and added a dash of colour, just to freshen it up a little bit! Hand printed in the UK on a WHITE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: BOLD AS LOVE - Black_By Si Scott
description: This little beauty is our second collaboration shirt with legendary illustrator Si Scott. It's a homage to one of Jimi Hendrix's more understated albums of the same name. We think you'll agree Si's indomitable style is really displayed to its fullest. I'm bold as love. Just ask the axis – he knows everything. Hand printed in the UK on a BLACK organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: BOLD AS LOVE_By Si Scott
description: This little beauty is our second collaboration shirt with legendary illustrator Si Scott. It's a homage to one of Jimi Hendrix's more understated albums of the same name. We think you'll agree Si's indomitable style is really displayed to its fullest. I'm bold as love. Just ask the axis – he knows everything. name: GOOD VIBRATIONS
description: "Ah! I love the colourful clothes she wears..." I’d love her too Brian, if she were wearing this little number! This shirt is giving me excitations; woo-ooo-hooo, good vibrations. Hand printed in the UK on a NAVY BLUE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: LIBERTÉ
description: Liberty. The freedom from control and restriction. The opportunity of thinking and speaking, according to choice. These are concepts that we hold dear at Origin68 - it allows us to bring you the designs that we do, amongst other things. Some people are less fortunate and this should not be forgotten. As a famous scholar once said; "You can take our trees, but you can never take our freedom!" Hand printed in the UK on a GREY TRI-BLEND organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: HUMAN BEING - Grey 5th Birthday Limited Edition
description: Time flies when you're having fun - Origin68 is 5 years old! Huzzah! To celebrate this we're taking one of our favourite designs and doing a special limited edition collectors version, complete with some lovely packaging, wooden hang tag and a storage box to keep it in. There will only be 50 ever created, so don't miss out! If us Humans came in packets (like pretty much everything does these days) we reckon they would look something like this. After all we're a bit like the usual stuff that comes in big boxes... We're fragile, need to be kept dry, handled with care... And kept the right way up! Especially after a couple of cheeky beers. You can be a walking talking human box... Maybe a beat box... But we'll leave that choice to you! Hand printed in the UK on a GREY organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: BANKS BURN YOUR MONEY
description: It'd probably be fair to say that our global banking system has had a bit of a mare these last few years. Just ask the Greeks... And the Spanish... And the Irish. Everyone. Credit crunches, Ponzi's, Libors... the list goes on and on. All in the pursuit of the Benjamins. They pretty much might as well have just shovelled all the dosh straight into a big furnance, chuffing on a fat cigar as they did it! This shirt is our second design inspired by the Student Uprising in Paris of May 68, it's interesting to see that the issues that existed then are still with us today. Hand printed in the UK on a WHITE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: KIND OF BLUE
description: Decorating the house and looking for a nice shade of blue? How about Kosmic Blue in the kitchen? Or Shotgun Blue in the bedroom? No? Maybe you just like the coming together of cracking music and a Pantone style colour chart? Here's the setlist - have you got them all!? Robert Johnson – Cross Road Blues Muddy Waters – Louisiana Blues B.B. King – Three O’Clock Blues Carl Perkins – Blue Suede Shoes Eddie Cochran – Summertime Blues Dave Brubeck Quartet – Blue Rondo A La Turk Ella Fitzgerald – The Devil And The Deep Blue Sea Bobby Vinton – Blue Velvet Son House – Death Letter Blues Jefferson Airplane – Blues From An Airplane 13th Floor Elevators – It’s All Over Now, Baby Blue Jimi Hendrix – Catfish Blues Johnny Cash – Folsom Prison Blues The Beatles – Yer Blues The Velvet Underground – Pale Blue Eyes Crosby, Stills & Nash – Suite: Judy Blue Eyes Nick Drake – Way To Blue Janis Joplin – Kozmic Blues Rodriguez – Establishment Blues The Doors – Roadhouse Blues Joni Mitchell – Blue The Allman Brothers Band – Statesboro Blues Marvin Gaye – Inner City Blues The Rolling Stones – I Got The Blues Neil Young – Revolution Blues Bob Dylan – Tangled Up In Blue Elvis Presley – Moody Blue Electric Light Orchestra – Mr Blue Sky Blondie – Union City Blue Elton John – I Guess That’s Why They Call It The Blues New Order – Blue Monday David Bowie – Blue Jean Prince – Computer Blue Madonna – True Blue Massive Attack – Blue Lines Guns N' Roses – Shotgun Blues Blur – Blue Jeans White Stripes – Blue Orchid The Charlatans – Blackened Blue Eyes Belle & Sebastian – The Blues Are Still Blue Fleet Foxes – Helplessness Blues Hand printed in the UK on a WHITE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: PANTUNE
description: Our second coming together of cracking music and a Pantone style colour chart, after 'Kind of Blue', a big favourite of ours. This time we've covered all the bases. So whatever colours you need to paint your house, we've got your back. Ruby Tuesday in the bathroom? No problem. The Green Manalishi in the kitchen? Awesome. Orange Crush in the bedroom? No, that might be a bit much! Here's the setlist - have you got them all!? Wu-Tang Clan - CREAM Crosby Stills Nash/Young - Cinnamon Girl The Temptations - Papa Was a Rolling Stone Blur - Coffee & TV Bob Dylan - Hazel Metallica - Enter Sandman Louis Armstrong - Mahogony Hall Stomp Van Morrison - Brown Eyed Girl Nick Drake - Pink Moon Grateful Dead - Sugar Magnolia MC5 - Ramblin' Rose Prince - Raspberry Berret The Stranglers - Peaches Brothers Johnson - Strawberry Letter #23 The Rolling Stones - Ruby Tuesday Kings Of Leon - Red Morning Light REM - Orange Crush Dave Brubeck Quartet - Tangerine Led Zepplin - The Lemon Song Jesus & Mary Chain - Just Like Honey INXS - Suicide Blonde Beatles - Mean Mr Mustard Joni Mitchell - Big Yellow Taxi Rush - Limelight The Cure - Mint Car Thin Lizzy - Emerald Herman Dune - 1, 2, 3, Apple Tree Fleetwood Mac - The Green Manalishi Marvin Gaye - Inner City Blues Duke Ellington - Azure Santana - Aquamarine Sonic Youth - Turquoise Boy Nina Simone - Mood Indigo Jeff Buckley - Lilac Wine The Kinks - Lavender Hill Jimi Hendrix - Purple Haze Grandmaster Flash - White Lines Visage - Fade To Grey AC/DC - Back In Black The Stone Roses - Fools Gold Hawkwind - Silver Machine The Pretenders - Brass In Pocket Hand printed in the UK on a WHITE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: ENJOY LIFE
description: Depending on who you listen to, there are many secrets to enjoying your life... love, a good job... er... gluten free snack bars... erm... Perhaps a t-shirt? Enjoy Life kids. Hand printed in the UK on a GREY TRIBLEND organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: THE DOVE_By Si Scott
description: This shirt needs no introduction...Ohh, go on then. This design is by the legendary Si Scott and displays a dove, the symbol of peace, in his amazingly highly detailed illustrative hand drawn style. Si is pretty much the grand master of intricate swirly designs. We're really proud to bring you this one! Enjoy. Hand printed in the UK on a WHITE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: DEAD AIR_By Steven Bonner
description: Have you ever thought about the invisible airwaves crackling with life and got a bit of a rush? We have. There are so many broadcast signals flying around out there, each telling its own story, flooding out into space... It’s practically littering. This typographical shirt shows air waves floating around, cluttering up the place… perhaps it would be better to have, Dead Air? Hand printed in the UK on a GREY TRIBLEND organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: CHARTING THE BEATLES_By Michael Deal
description: OK, let me ask you this... What were Ringo, George, Paul , John and Grant* doing in March 1964? What's that? You don't know? How about December 1966? No? For shame. That's where this little beauty comes in. This shirt charts the work of the Beatles from 1963 through to the end of 1966, when they were making some of their best work. You can cut it out and use it as a dartboard too... but... please don't. * A lot of people don't know Grant was in The Beatles, he wrote all the catchy numbers, but Ringo was jealous.** **This statement may not be historically accurate. Hand printed in the UK on a BLACK organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: GO PLAY_By Stuart Whitton
description: 'Go Play', by Stuart Whitton, is a hand-drawn typographic illustration, the words being constructed from pencil shavings! And yes, it took ages. We feel the design is an ode to our childhood - exploring the notion of play. Like a lot of small kids, we always enjoyed (over) sharpening pencils, especially when the sharpener was one of those handle driven ones or the luxurious motorised variety... Enough reminiscing! Hand printed in the UK on a WHITE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: PARIS '68
description: Yes indeed, we're talking crazy French beatniks who don't mind whipping up a funk or two for The MAN up on Capitol Hill. We're rather partial to our cousins across the ol'briney and surely you’ve got to admire them, they’re not stupid. When they don’t like stuff they get up off their arses and kick up a right fuss about it! Not like the rest of us who just have a good old moan and then sit back down on the sofa for Strictly-Factor or some other brain nullifying crap. May 68 in Paris was one of those iconic moments where the people came together and took on the powers that control them and through not inconsiderable sacrifice changed things for the better. Vive la revolution! Hand printed in the UK on a LIGHT GREY organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: INTERNAL ERROR_By Melvin Galapon
description: Prince once blamed it on something in the water, messing with his computeé shizzle, but we know pretty much anything can throw a spanner in the pipes causing a massive internal errors. We're pleased to say that Mr Melvin Galapon has crafted this shirt; a tribute to the mighty error! ** Our legal eagle, Eddy, recommended a legal disclaimer, so this shirt comes with a special Origin68 public health warning... We will not be held liable if you stare at this one for any longer than 6.8 seconds. It has be known to melt eyes/minds, sofas and small reptiles. Hand printed in the UK on a BLACK organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: PRISMS
description: Like a circle in a spiral Like a wheel within a wheel Never ending or beginning On an ever-spinning reel As the images unwind Like the circles that you find In the windmills of your mind Hand printed in the UK on a WHITE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: CONTENTS MAY VARY IN COLOUR
description: Have you ever bought something and the packaging has advised that the contents may vary in colour? Embrace the lottery we say. It’s much like us human beans really. Hand printed in the UK on a BLACK organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: THINK FORWARD & LOOK BACK_By Rizki Katamsi & Mymutas
description: Someone once said; "the longer you look back, the further you can look forward." That's a concept that we hold dear at Origin68 Towers throughout all our work. Even when we're making the tea. It leads to over-brewing. This hand illustrated design by Mymutas and Rizki Katamsi encapsulates that philosophy… It looks sweet too… Pop pop, two for one! Hand printed in the UK on a TRIBLEND organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: THINK FORWARD & LOOK BACK II_By Rizki Katamsi
description: Our second hand illustrated design from Indonesia’s finest, Rizki Katamsi. Again, challenging us all to think forward and look back. This shirt has got a little bit of a Cubist flavour for all you art lovers out there. There's also a hidden 68 in there... Can you see it? Hand printed in the UK on a NATURAL organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: HIGHER THAN THE SUN_By Steven Bonner
description: My brightest stars my inner light let it guide me... In this case it guided us to MR STEVEN BONNER's front door. He kindly invited us in for afternoon tea and scones. As soon as we saw the design we knew we had to have it. Not only is it a great piece of typography but it also reminds us of the super Primal Scream song of the same name. Hand printed in the UK on a NAVY BLUE organic tshirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: THE 27 CLUB
description: Jones, Johnson, Hendrix, Joplin, Cobain, Morrison, Winehouse; what do they all have in common? The 27 Club is a name for a group of influential musicians who all died tragically at the age of 27. This shirt pays homage to their achievements. Featured are; Brian Jones - Founding member of The Rolling Stones. Robert Johnson - The most important blues singer that ever lived. Jimi Hendrix - The greatest electric guitarist in music history. Janis Joplin - The Queen of Rock and Roll. Kurt Cobain - Lead singer of Nirvana. Jim Morrison - Lead singer of The Doors. Amy Winehouse - Eclectic R&B, soul and jazz singer. R.I.P. Hand printed in the UK on a BLACK organic tshirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: THE WORLD IN YOUR EYES_By Anthony Aguero
description: This is our shirt collaboration with Mr Anthony Aguero, of Costa Rica. We were massive fans of the psychedelic nature of this design… Perhaps that’s how the world looks in our eyes - we have visions of Roger Moore in a milk float with a obese Swiss terrapin who calls himself Charles, greasing about Monte Carlo wearing one of these bad boys! Hmmm, better lay off the nachos. How's The World In Your Eyes? Hand printed in the UK on a WHITE organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: MEXICO '68
description: As you all probably know by now, there was some big event on in London in the summer of 2012. To commemorate this momentous event we've brought you this design which celebrates the magnitude of the occasion! This shirt is our homage to the iconic poster designed for the Mexico games in 1968. Hand printed in the UK on a GREY TRI-BLEND organic t-shirt. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: THE DOVE iPHONE 4/4S/5/5S COVER_By Si Scott
description:
This design is by the legendary Si Scott and displays a dove, the symbol of peace, in his amazingly highly detailed illustrative hand drawn style.
 
Si is pretty much the grand master of intricate swirly designs. We're really proud to bring you this one! Enjoy.
 
Each cover is precision-cut for a perfect fit and because we use real Forest Stewardship Council certified wood and not synthetic wood or lookalike stickers, each cover is totally unique and ages beautifully with use. Each is made using a multi-step hand finishing process to achieve a beautiful finish that brings out the beauty of each skin.
 
Anti-residue adhesive makes the cover easy to apply and won’t damage the phone if removed.

Each cover is also supplied with a screen protective film.

The cover is compatible with the iPhone 4/4S or 5/5S (choose option). It is NOT compatible with the iPhone 5C.
 
iPhone not included!
 
*WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

description:

I’d love her too Brian, if she had this little number adorning her phone! It'd be giving me excitations; woo-ooo-hooo, good vibrations. Must be on silent...

Each cover is also supplied with a screen protective film.
The cover is compatible with the iPhone 4/4S or 5/5S (choose option). It is NOT compatible with the iPhone 5C.

iPhone not included!

name: HOT DRINK MUG
description:
We've all gone a bit Ronseal with this. And I don't mean perma-tanned. Oh no, it's a mug that does exactly what it says on the tin... I mean ceramic, er mug. It's got hot drink in it. 

By the way ours is a tea, white with one sugar, if you're putting the kettle on.

WARNING: Contains Hot Liquids

*We ship worldwide!

name: GOOD VIBRATIONS BAG
description: "Ah! I love the colourful clothes she wears..." I’d love her too Brian, if she was out shopping with this little number! This is totes giving me excitations; woo-ooo-hooo, good vibrations. Hand printed in the UK on an organic tote bag. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: ENJOY LIFE BAG
description: Depending on who you listen to, there are many secrets to enjoying your life... love, a good job... er... gluten free snack bars... erm... Perhaps a shopping tote bag? Enjoy Life kids. Hand printed in the UK on an organic tote bag. *WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: SHOPPING BEING BAG
description: This is our Human Being shirt inspired shopping bag. We have created the perfect organic packaging for all your shopping goodies. Forget about all those dirty little plastic bags... Yes the ones you keep hoarding in your cupboard on the off chance that you might actually recycle them (until you realise that there isn't actually anywhere within a ten mile radius to take them), because we are bringing you this little organic number to carry your vegetables home in. WARNING: May contain nuts *We ship worldwide

name: CONSUME BAG
description: So you've bought a few bits, but you need something to carry them in. This is the bag for you! It's printed on our usual organic tote bags so all your goodies will feel right at home. WARNING: May contain light swearing. Hand printed in the UK on a organic tote bag. *We ship worldwide

name: THE DOVE BAG_By Si Scott
description: Have you ever wondered what might happen if a dove flew into a shopping bag? What's that? No?! Really. Well, don't go into the world and try trapping one. It's just not on. Anyway we've saved you the job, by doing one of those artistic interpretation thingys. And here it is. You can carry all your shopping... in a Dove... hand illustrated by Si Scott. Who'd have thought it? Hand printed in the UK on a organic tote bag. *We ship worldwide

name: BADGE PACK - MIXED BAG
description:
When we were putting together our three badge/pin packs there were certain designs that we just had to use and could not leave out. So we put them into our mixed bag!

The Dove
Enjoy Life
Mexico '68
Prisms

*WE SHIP WORLDWIDE

name: BADGE PACK - PANTUNE
description:

We have;

Little Red Corvette - Prince
Mellow Yellow - Donovan
Green Onions - Booker T. & The M.G.'s

The beauty of these is that you can even colour co-ordinate your outfits... and match that colour you want to paint your walls!
